{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Clipboard.writeText()","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Clipboard/writeText","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Clipboard_API\">Clipboard API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Clipboard\"><code>Clipboard</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Clipboard/read\"><code>read()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Clipboard/readText\"><code>readText()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Clipboard/write\"><code>write()</code></a></li><li><em><code>writeText()</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>継承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Clipboard API に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ClipboardEvent\"><code>ClipboardEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ClipboardItem\"><code>ClipboardItem</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Navigator/clipboard\"><code>Navigator.clipboard</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>\n  <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Clipboard\"><code>Clipboard</code></a> インターフェイスの <strong><code>writeText()</code></strong>\n  メソッドは、指定されたテキスト文字列をシステムのクリップボードの書き込みます。テキストは <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Clipboard/read\" title=\"read()\"><code>read()</code></a> または <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Clipboard/readText\" title=\"readText()\"><code>readText()</code></a> を使って読み戻すことができます。\n</p>\n<p><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Permissions_API\">権限 API</a> の <code>\"clipboard-write\"</code> 権限は、ページがアクティブなタブにあるときに自動的に付与されます。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"構文","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token function\">writeText</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>newClipText<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"引数","title":"引数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"newcliptext\"><code>newClipText</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>クリップボードに書き込む文字列。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"返値","title":"返値","isH3":true,"content":"<p>クリップボードの内容が更新されると解決されるプロミス (<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise\"><code>Promise</code></a>)。呼び出し元がクリップボードへの書き込み権限を持っていない場合、このプロミスは拒否されます。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>この例では、クリップボードの内容を \"&lt;empty clipboard&gt;\" という文字列に設定します。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>navigator<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>clipboard<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">writeText</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"&lt;empty clipboard&gt;\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">then</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">/* clipboard successfully set */</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">/* clipboard write failed */</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"仕様書","id":"仕様書","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/clipboard-apis/#dom-clipboard-writetext","title":"Clipboard API and events"}],"query":"api.Clipboard.writeText"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"ブラウザーの互換性","isH3":false,"query":"api.Clipboard.writeText","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Clipboard/writeText/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"関連情報","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Clipboard_API\">クリップボード API</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://async-clipboard-api.glitch.me/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Async Clipboard API demo on Glitch</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://web.dev/async-clipboard/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Image support for Async Clipboard article</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"構文"},{"text":"例","id":"例"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"仕様書"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"ブラウザーの互換性"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"関連情報"}],"summary":"Clipboard インターフェイスの writeText()\n  メソッドは、指定されたテキスト文字列をシステムのクリップボードの書き込みます。テキストは read() または readText() を使って読み戻すことができます。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Clipboard.writeText()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Clipboard.writeText()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Clipboard.writeText()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/clipboard/writetext","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/clipboard/writetext/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Clipboard","title":"Clipboard"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Clipboard/writeText","title":"Clipboard.writeText()"}],"pageTitle":"Clipboard.writeText() - We